    <!-- SECTION 3: KSM-66 vs SENSORIL -->
    <h2>KSM-66 vs Sensoril vs Generic Ashwagandha for Anxiety</h2>

    <p>Not all ashwagandha is the same. The extract type determines whether you will experience clinically meaningful anxiety reduction or simply consume an expensive placebo. There are three categories of ashwagandha on the market, and the differences are substantial.</p>

